<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.231.100894.figure101>
    dc:description "Figure 101. Solanum nigrescens A new shoot B flower C inflorescence with mature fruit (A-C Ventura 672). Illustration by L. Ribulgo. Previously published in Knapp et al. (2019: 81)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/897562" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.231.100894.figure102>
    dc:description "Figure 102. Solanum nigrescens A leaves B flowering branch C inflorescence with flowers at full anthesis D developing fruits (A-D Amith et al. F 0055). Photos by M. Gorostiza Salazar. Previously published in Knapp et al. (2019: 82)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/897563" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.231.100894.figure103>
    dc:description "Figure 103. Distribution map of Solanum nigrescens in South America. For distribution in North and Central America and the Caribbean, see Knapp et al. (2019: 84)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/897564" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

